### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Ping
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ping

### Create Coupon Book
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "name": "Verano 2026",
  "description": "Cupones de descuento verano",
  "maxRedeemsPerUser": 1
}

### Get All Coupon Books
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-books

### Get Coupon Book by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-books/4d28b6c6-9183-47aa-9140-4e5f5fcf101e

### Update Coupon Book (replace {id} with actual ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-books/4d28b6c6-9183-47aa-9140-4e5f5fcf101e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Generate Random Coupon Codes
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-codes/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "76fafd1e-332b-47bf-a345-a60ef2e65b23",
  "quantity": 100,
  "prefix": "SUMMER2026",
  "length": 6
}

### Upload Bulk Coupon Codes
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-codes/upload
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "76fafd1e-332b-47bf-a345-a60ef2e65b23",
  "codes": ["CODE001", "CODE002", "CODE003", "CODE004", "CODE005"]
}

### Get Codes for Coupon Book
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-codes/book/76fafd1e-332b-47bf-a345-a60ef2e65b23?limit=50&offset=0

### Get Available Codes Only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/coupon-codes/book/76fafd1e-332b-47bf-a345-a60ef2e65b23?status=AVAILABLE

